228
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:33,114
He doesn't want to
declare bankruptcy.

229
00:08:33,149 --> 00:08:36,284
He wants you to fight for him.

230
00:08:36,319 --> 00:08:38,720
Then he's come to me
on the right day.

231
