239
00:08:57,540 --> 00:08:59,007
Don't let the door hit you
on the way out.

240
00:08:59,041 --> 00:09:00,642
- What?
- You heard me.

241
00:09:00,676 --> 00:09:03,411
Only one of us is facing
bankruptcy and it isn't me.

242
